Definitions
-----------

"Licensed Work" means the ProIdentity Mail source code, binaries, scripts,
documentation, and related files in this repository.

"Commercial Hosted Service Use" means offering the Licensed Work, a modified
version, or a substantially similar derivative as a paid or revenue-generating
hosted service, SaaS product, managed mail service, cloud marketplace image,
MSP offering, commercial email/groupware platform, or third-party hosting
service.

"Internal Use" means running the Licensed Work for your own personal systems,
your own organization, your own employees, or your own customers when the
Licensed Work itself is not offered as a paid hosted product or managed mail
service.

